review:
Thank you Dr.Vanaja and staff for the great and quality work you are doing. My family and I am very much pleased with your quality service and care. 

She is a highly qualified and the way she treats is like a family member. Whole staff are supportive and helpful. I must say CROWN CLINIC is one of the best clinics in town, and its truly for Service oriented. Clinic is very clean and hygienic.

She took utmost care in identifying the infection under my lower front teeth and treating with the help of finest maxillofacial surgeon (Dr.Amit) for syst removal in her clinic itself with reasonable cost. Entire surgery tool almost an hour and she gave me great confidence and deliver the best in treating it.

Thanks again doc for My Mom's pain less RCT treatment for broken tooth and fixing CAP. Overall treatment was done with extreme care. 

She always makes me and my family comfortable. I EXTREMELY recommended Dr. Vanaja for everyone who is having dental problems. Glad I met Dr.Vanaja for my dental care!

review: *** ****** **** ** *** **** ****** * **** ********** Not only is she excellent in her profession but also very friendly and very patient. A rare quality that you see in doctors of todays world. I went with lot of apprehensions but the doctor took me into confidence and suggested the best steps that she will take going forward with my treatment of my tooth and gum problem. I can trust her blindly for the best results. My capped tooth extraction was done smoothly today without any pain and with almost care. She mentioned each and every thing in detail and also mentioned the do's and dont's with patience.  I will definitely recommend her for all the parents with kids who have dental problems. She will be THE BEST choice. Trust me. Thank you soooo much Doctor.
reply_text: Many thanks for the feedback sir

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: I was extremely comfortable consulting with Dr.Vanaja regarding my wisdom tooth extraction. My wisdom teeth were impacted and I was really nervous about getting them taken out. She invested a great deal of effort in finding me the best surgeon in town to undergo the procedure at her clinic. I was walked through the entire procedure with great care. I was given different options for undergoing the surgery which I truly appreciate. Her clinic is well equipped and is highly professional. She made sure to check up on me from time to time post surgery. Dr.Vanaja is extremely patient, cleared all my doubts and anxieties before and after the surgery. She pays extra attention and informs you about proper dental hygiene. I trust her as my doctor and would highly recommend going to her clinic.
reply_text: Thank you Vihanga & I promise to look after the plant:)
